overview: Kiara Mia is youthful, sensual, sexual starlet whose fame arose from a sex tape release with a former hot artist Ray. Kiara Mia has also skyrocketed her two sisters Court and Chloe alongside her for the stargazing ride. Meanwhile their mother Kris manages Kiara Mia while balancing the rest of the household.
title: Keeping Up with Kiara Mia
